title: “Cards”
author: VD
content_html: Another strange potential McCann-Podesta connection. Who is the little girl in the picture and why does she so closely resemble the computer simulation of what Madeleine McCann would look like as a preteen? And is the FBI investigating this or is it also part of Comey’s apparent whitewash?
